TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(2,15,1);

BEGIN_TEXT
Find the equation of the tangent line to the curve
 \( y =    $a1 x e^x  \) at the point \( ( 0 , 0 ) \).
The equation of this tangent line can be written in the form \( y = mx+b \).
Find \(m\) and \(b\). $BR$BR

 \( m =\) \{ans_rule(30)\} $BR
 \( b =\) \{ans_rule(30)\}

END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp($a1));
ANS(num_cmp(0));

